{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to update the appearance of the user location annotation. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method is called by the associated map view when it has determined that the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user location annotation needs to be updated. This can happen in response to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user interaction, a change in the user’s location, when the user tracking mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"changes, or when the viewport changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"During user interaction with the map, this method may be called many","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"times to update the user location annotation. Therefore, your implementation of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method should be as lightweight as possible to avoid negatively affecting"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance."}]}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNUserLocationAnnotationView(im)update","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"update"}],"title":"update","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h#L59"},"fragment